ingredientsDesc:
test strips in plastic reaction troughs, nitrocellulose membranes 
coated with allergen material on 20 test fields
washing buffer concentrate (TRIS/NaCl, contains 0.099% NaN3), 
yields 1×500 ml washing buffer, pH=7.5 (20 ml)
detector antibody (bottle with white cap), ready for use (4 ml) 
with biotin conjugated anti-human IgE antibodies, polyclonal, contains 0.099% NaN3
streptavidin-conjugate (bottle with red cap), ready for use (4 ml) 
streptavidin conjugated with alkaline phosphatase 
contains 0.02% methylisothiazolinone and 0.02% bromonitrodexan
Substrate (bottle with blue cap), ready for use(4 ml) 
BCIP/ NBT (bromochloroindolyl phosphate/ Nitro Blue Tetrazolium),
